<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Switch Dashboard</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #f8fbff, #e2ecf5);
      color: #2c3e50;
      padding: 2rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #1a2b49;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
    }

    header p {
      color: #5a6780;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
    }
    a{
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
    }
    .container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 1100px;
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      animation: slideUp 1s ease-out;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 1.25rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .card h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #1c2d4a;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      color: #4a5662;
    }

    .card button {
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #007bff, #0056b3);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card button:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #0056b3, #003e80);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #7c8a9c;
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @keyframes slideUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      body {
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      header h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 1.2rem;
      }

      .card h3 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>QoS Implementation & Dynamic Traffic Management in SDN-Based Campus Networks</h1>
    <p>
      Department of Electrical Engineering â€¢ Broadband Communication Networks<br/>
      <strong>Miracle Chidinma Nnabuko</strong> (NNBMIR001)
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Switch One</h3>
      <p>This is core or master switch, it performs routing</p>
      <button>Manipulate Switch One Data</button>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Switch Two</h3>
      <p>Host one and Host two are connected to Switch Two</p>
      <button><a href="/switchtwo">Manipulate Switch Two Data</a> </button>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Switch Three</h3>
      <p>Host three and host four are connected to Switch Three</p>
      <button>Manipulate Switch Three Data</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%-include('partials/footer')%>
 
</body>
</html>
